cian, an emergency electrician, a NICEIC-approved contractor, a NAPIT-registered electrician, an ECA member, an EV charger installer, a solar panel installer, a rewire specialist, a fire alarm engineer, a testing and inspection specialist, or a self-employed spark — the AI handles every text message. It covers every electrical enquiry: rewiring, partial rewiring, consumer unit upgrades, fuse board replacements, RCD installations, socket additions, lighting installations, LED upgrades, outdoor lighting, security lighting, EICR testing, electrical inspection reports, PAT testing, emergency lighting, fire alarm installation, smoke detector installation, EV charger installation, solar panel installation, battery storage, three-phase installations, commercial fit-outs, and electrical maintenance contracts. The AI captures every compliance deadline, fault description, and photo and delivers the complete lead to your phone." },
